      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Chakra Control </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 1 (Spell Level 1)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 1</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 14 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 2 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 13</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You focus your senses and become able to immediately tell if a creature in range is poisoned or not by reading their body's functions. A successful Wisdom check (DC 20) can determine which kind of poison is affecting such a target.</p>\n\n\n\n",
